Quickstrike:





Quickstrike lifted his head up and stood up tall, seeing Black 
Arachnia approach. He always came attention and tried to look 
impressive when she came around to him. He still kept his ankles 
crossed and shoulder leaned against the frame of the threshold. His 
optics brightened at her, even if it was about Dark Mouse.

"Yeah?" he said lowly. "What about it?"
